column2: it was plated very well. My entire dish was warm and very fresh. The tacos were stuffed with cheese
column4: and chorizo. The potatoes were warm and perfectly crispy yet flavorful. The black beans were some of the best I ever had. Overall
column5: an amazing breakfast that I would wait 40 minites for over and over again. My boyfriend's dished looked equally delicious and he enjoyed it. I was stuffed after finishing
column6: it was a perfect amount of food. The bill was less than 20 dollars
column7: which is excellent considering the quality. I WILL be visiting again soon.
